---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="共建我们" description="欢迎大学生提交真实专业学习体验，帮助更多人少走弯路">
  <section class="py-10 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">

      <!-- 页面头 -->
      <div class="text-center mb-10">
        <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">共建我们</h1>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">让你的真实经历，帮助更多高中生少走弯路</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 mt-2">公益项目 · 核心功能免费 · 不做商业导流</p>
      </div>

      <!-- 为什么需要你 -->
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm mb-6">
        <h2 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-3">🎓 为什么需要你</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
          官方专业介绍往往太"官方"——列培养方案、说就业方向，但高中生最想知道的其实是：<strong class="text-slate-700">这个专业到底学什么课？做不做实验？累不累？和高中有什么不同？</strong>
        </p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
          只有真正在读或毕业的大学生，才能回答这些问题。
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- 三类共建入口 -->
      <div class="space-y-4 mb-8">

        <!-- 入口一：补充专业内容 -->
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 mb-4">
            <span class="text-2xl shrink-0">📝</span>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">我想补充专业内容</h3>
              <p class="text-xs text-slate-400">你是某专业的大学生或研究生？分享你的真实学习体验</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <ul class="space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-600 mb-4 ml-9">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-primary mt-0.5 shrink-0">●</span>
              <span>大学课程真实难度、实验内容、课外时间分配</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-primary mt-0.5 shrink-0">●</span>
              <span>和想象中最大的差异——哪些是来了才知道的</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-primary mt-0.5 shrink-0">●</span>
              <span>选课建议：哪些课重要、哪些坑要避开</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-primary mt-0.5 shrink-0">●</span>
              <span>毕业去向：考研还是就业，实际体验如何</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <a href="https://v.wjx.cn/vm/eot33he.aspx"
             target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
             onclick="return confirm('即将跳转到问卷星（补充专业内容，匿名填写），是否继续？')"
             class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-primary text-white text-sm font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-primary/90 transition-colors shadow-sm ml-9">
            📋 填写内容共建表单（匿名）
            <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- 入口二：纠错 -->
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 mb-4">
            <span class="text-2xl shrink-0">✏️</span>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">我想纠错</h3>
              <p class="text-xs text-slate-400">发现专业详情页有错误或不准确的地方？</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <ul class="space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-600 mb-4 ml-9">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-primary mt-0.5 shrink-0">●</span>
              <span>专业详情页的专业方向、学习内容、主要课程描述不准确</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-primary mt-0.5 shrink-0">●</span>
              <span>推荐分组逻辑有问题（你觉得应该进优先区但没有）</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-primary mt-0.5 shrink-0">●</span>
              <span>任何你觉得会误导高中生的地方</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <a href="https://v.wjx.cn/vm/wFaDlmJ.aspx"
             target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
             onclick="return confirm('即将跳转到问卷星（纠错反馈，匿名填写），是否继续？')"
             class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-white border border-primary text-primary text-sm font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-primary-light transition-colors ml-9">
            ✏️ 填写纠错表单（匿名）
            <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- 入口三：测试题优化 -->
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 mb-4">
            <span class="text-2xl shrink-0">🧪</span>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">我想参与测试题优化</h3>
              <p class="text-xs text-slate-400">觉得某道题问得不对、选项有诱导性、或缺少某个方向？</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <ul class="space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-600 mb-4 ml-9">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-primary mt-0.5 shrink-0">●</span>
              <span>某道题暴露了学科名称，让学生直接知道答案</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-primary mt-0.5 shrink-0">●</span>
              <span>某道题的选项对某些方向有明显的倾向性</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-primary mt-0.5 shrink-0">●</span>
              <span>你觉得缺少某个方向或场景的题目</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-primary mt-0.5 shrink-0">●</span>
              <span>愿意作为内测用户长期提供反馈</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <a href="https://v.wjx.cn/vm/mXrf117.aspx"
             target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
             onclick="return confirm('即将跳转到问卷星（测试题反馈，匿名填写），是否继续？')"
             class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-white border border-primary text-primary text-sm font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-primary-light transition-colors ml-9">
            🧪 填写题目反馈表单（匿名）
            <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- 内容审核说明 -->
      <div class="bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 mb-6">
        <h2 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-3">🔍 内容审核说明</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-600">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-slate-400 mt-0.5 shrink-0">—</span>
            <span>提交的内容会经过人工审核，确保真实、友善、不制造焦虑才会展示</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-slate-400 mt-0.5 shrink-0">—</span>
            <span>我们反对任何形式的"劝退"或"无脑吹"，只支持客观、中立、有参考价值的分享</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-slate-400 mt-0.5 shrink-0">—</span>
            <span>审核结果会在 3 个工作日内通过邮件/飞书通知（如果你留了联系方式）</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- 隐私声明 -->
      <div class="bg-green-50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-green-100 mb-6">
        <h2 class="font-semibold text-green-800 mb-3">🔒 你的隐私很安全</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-1.5 text-sm text-green-700">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-green-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0">✓</span>
            <span>不收集姓名、手机号、身份证、准考证号</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-green-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0">✓</span>
            <span>不收集具体分数、成绩、排名</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-green-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0">✓</span>
            <span>共建内容仅用于"专业不迷路"网站，不用于商业目的</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-green-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0">✓</span>
            <span>如果你留下联系方式（如邮箱/飞书），仅用于审核结果通知，不会用于任何营销</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- 联系我们 -->
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200">
        <h2 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-3">💬 先联系我们</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
          如果你有共建意向或任何建议，欢迎通过以下方式联系我们：
        </p>
        <div class="mt-3 space-y-1.5">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
            <span class="w-5 h-5 rounded bg-blue-50 flex items-center justify-center text-xs shrink-0">🐧</span>
            <span class="font-medium text-slate-700">QQ：</span>
            <code class="text-sm bg-slate-100 px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-slate-700">1531371420</code>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
            <span class="w-5 h-5 rounded bg-green-50 flex items-center justify-center text-xs shrink-0">💬</span>
            <span class="font-medium text-slate-700">微信：</span>
            <code class="text-sm bg-slate-100 px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-slate-700">helloworld-dlx</code>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
            <span class="w-5 h-5 rounded bg-purple-50 flex items-center justify-center text-xs shrink-0">🐙</span>
            <span class="font-medium text-slate-700">GitHub：</span>
            <a href="https://github.com/helloworld-dlx" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary hover:underline">@helloworld-dlx</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>